    <h2 {...{
      "id": "hooks"
    }}>{`Hooks`}</h2>
    <p>{`ORY Kratos allows you to configure hooks that run before and after a Login or
Registration Request is generated. This may be helpful if you'd like to restrict
logins to IPs coming from your internal network or other logic.`}</p>
    <p>{`For more information about hooks please read the
`}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/kratos/docs/next/self-service/hooks/index"
      }}>{`Hook Documentation`}</a>{`.`}</p>
